examples.en: They have fresh bread every morning at the bakery.
I happened upon the most wonderful bakery not very far from here.
The bakery offers a nice selection of breads and pastries.
Besides its famous cakes, the bakery also makes delicious breads and cookies.
In November, Clean's bakery produced 50 percent more bread than normal.
The bakery business has changed beyond all recognition in the last 10 years.
